fields.name: Carpenter Jeans
fields.description: Carpenter jeans often come with multiple pockets and a loose fit, offering a practical and roomy option for those who need functionality and style.

fields.name: White Overdyed Printed Jean
fields.description:
Introducing the StagmenFashion Overdyed print Jean  where classic denim meets contemporary style to redefine casual comfort and fashion-forward flair. These jeans are not just an outfit; they're a statement, a testament to your unique fashion sensibilities.

Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, these overdyed print jeans boast a roomy and relaxed fit, making them a standout addition to your wardrobe. The relaxed silhouette is carefully balanced to strike the perfect harmony between comfort and style. The StagmenFashion Overdyed print Jean features a high-rise waist and a loose, wide-leg design that exudes a sense of effortless coolness.
